â›‘ï¸ 9. docs/grounding_protocols.md

# Grounding Protocols

Used by SPS De-escalator:

- 4-6 breathing or box breathing
- Posture reset
- Temperature shift (cold water, air)
- Object focus with tactile anchor
- Slow head rotation (vestibular reset)
- Naming 5+ physical objects in current environment

Goal:
return the operator to **immediate physical reality**, not narratives or symbols.


