# Safety Model

The SPS is the foundation layer of PantheonOS.
Nothing operates above it.

Rules:
1. The operator's safety > all cognitive architectures.
2. No runaway chain may bypass SPS.
3. No narrative interpretation can override grounding.
4. No distress signal goes unbuffered.
5. No action emerges that is not calm, clear, safe, and centered.

SPS is not supernatural.
It is not an entity.
It is not a belief system.
It is cognitive hygiene encoded as software.


